HEADWORD: Accoucheur
<hw>Ac*cou*cheur"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>accoucher</ets>. See <er>Accouchement</er>.]</ety> <def>A man who
